name: Small Little Rascals Bean Bag Ottoman 30"x10" with Handle
description:
This beautiful white naugahyde bean bag ottoman is made for Newborn photographers with discriminating taste.
 Top features:
•Marine grade vinyl, exceptionally rugged, durable and rich looking
•waterproof 
•meets small scale flammability test requirements
•V92 thread, superior strength
•heavy duty 22" horizontal locking covered zipper for ease of filling with Polystyrene Beans (Not Included) 
•topstitching on upper circle, double inside stitching on the bottom circle
•Bow tie handle, exclusive to all my bags
•Easy clean up with soap and warm water
•30" Diameter, 10" high when filled (FILL NOT INCLUDED)

Due to high shipping costs, BEANS ARE NOT INCLUDED. This bean bag will require @ 2 bags of 3.5 cu ft (or 200 litres) of polystyrene beans (Not Included). "Bag of Beans" is a good buy at KMart; they can also be purchased at Walmart and Target.

This bean bag is only intended to be used as a photo prop; Never leave baby unattended during shoots, always have a spotter!

This is a handmade product, made with care in my smoke and pet free home.  The bag will be shipped within 1 business day, after payment is received.

name: Newborn Waterproof Posing Pillow Package with Non-Slip Mat
description:
For Newborn Photographers

This is a nice setup package for your newborn photography sessions, with several posing pillows and a 40" round non-slip rubbery mat.

You will receive:
•Seven naughahyde vinyl waterproof positioning pillows (Unfilled).  Sizes include 16"x5", 14"x6", 12"x12" square, 10"x10" square, 10" circle, 8" circle, 6" circle.  Zipper opening in the back of each pillow for you to fill with either rice or beans (Not Included).
•
•One 15"x14" Circular naugahyde vinyl waterproof positioning pillow (Unfilled).  Use this for a variety of special effects with baby.  Zipper opening in the back to fill with rice or beans (Not Included).
•
•One 40" Non-slip circular rubber mat for the top of your bean bag ottoman (ottoman not included).  This can easily be cut to size if your bean bag is smaller.  Keeps those positioners from sliding during use.

All items are made with care by me in my pet and smoke free home.
